{
  "texts": [
    "Further refinement of these features involves incorporating DWT into the architecture.",
    "The DWT decomposes the image features of CNN outputs in the spatial and frequency domains.",
    "This decomposition will enable the model to learn fine-grained details and high-level patterns effectively, which are also very important in medical imaging for finding subtle abnormalities like polyps or cancerous tissues.",
    "Hence, DWT will definitely contribute much to enhancing the feature representation, thereby improving classification performance, especially for complex classes.",
    "The integration of DWT ascertains those critical spatial details, often lost during standard feature extraction, are preserved and accentuated."
  ]
}